caption: I think it is a place where you can buy products that represent France the most. This shop is right to the National Assembly where you can purchase items used in the National Assembly. The price is reasonable and not expensive, I think they are suitable for souvenirs.

A huge thank you to all the staff of the National Assembly store, who always welcome you with a smile, who are at your disposal to provide you with details on the various quality products presented in the store... French parliament souvenir shop I bought socks that have "left" and "right" written on the left and right sides.  There are also many other stylish goods. Recommended for people who are tired of ordinary souvenirs.
